    "Automated segmentation tools driven by AI streamline the analysis of fetal anatomy, improving consistency in detecting anomalies such as vascular defects and cardiac malformations [61].",
    "This automation not only alleviates the cognitive burden on clinicians but also democratizes access to high-quality diagnostics through telemedicine platforms and portable devices [44,46].",
